Virginia Valli https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Valli 0 Virginia Valli (January 18, 1895 – September 24, 1968) was an American stage and film actress whose motion picture career started in the silent film era and lasted until the beginning of the sound film era of the 1930s.
